        <h4 class="headline">Tepperâs Market Moving History</h4>
		        <div class="caption-video">
                <div class="summary-credit">
            <p class="summary">Dominic Chu of CNBC looks back at past market moving calls by David Tepper, the billionaire hedge fund manager.</p>
            <span class="credit video-credit" itemprop="copyrightHolder">
